{"tid":2451233,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"90後 whisky/beerpong暨日頭健康活動谷","createTime":"2021-03-18T03:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T03:18:54.000Z","uid":225783,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"59c34a6d07f726d8ca914e6dadb0804e9f32e473","tid":2451233,"uid":225783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:14:10.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家入黎識下大家五湖四海 九龍新界既朋友<br />\n得閒入黎吹下水<br />\n有幾個admin恆常搞下活動<br />\n個谷長期控制40人以內<br />\n<br />\n因為限聚令既關係<br />\n而家只會定期搞日間健康活動聯誼 如行山、打羽毛球、飯聚，Happy Hour等<br />\n希望疫情過後大家一齊飲通頂啦<br />\n<br />\n單身既有伴侶既都歡迎入黎架<br />\n只要你肯出聚既 都歡迎你隨時即興搞聚<br />\n鍾意9up/識朋友/飲野/運動下 埋黎填個form啦<br />\n<br />\n傳送門:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsQtsHqgahUy6dTUYXXc9z0NTW9IO0UbM3uq_18GJL3kWWXA/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScsQtsHqgahUy6dTUYXXc9z0NTW9IO0UbM3uq_18GJL3kWWXA%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2dmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=5436d609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsQtsHqgahUy6dTUYXXc9z0NTW9IO0UbM3uq_18GJL3kWWXA/viewform?usp=sf_link</a>"},{"pid":"29a83a3d70426e3b64b3e0e071f97bdef664c959","tid":2451233,"uid":225783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:45:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e81bdd0488ed727cd6330fa5e02153c88bcfa969","tid":2451233,"uid":225783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:07:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b0298d7b6b43dd511d0f66610c38c2a1fc9e1f4f","tid":2451233,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e81bdd0488ed727cd6330fa5e02153c88bcfa969","tid":2451233,"uid":225783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:07:06.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"填完都唔撚加"},{"pid":"484bddcc7673d838f0b75f1ef34ad9d9fd670e11","tid":2451233,"uid":225783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite